    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This is a fire based rain spell. It will do constand direct damage as long as the target is under the fall of fire rain.<BR><EM>Need mana info</EM><BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>Rune of Conception, Rune of Solusek Ro, Rune of Cyclone
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
